OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778193328
OL,3,CBritish crew member evacuated from
OL,4,Chantavirus ship 'doing well'
OL,6,FProfessor Robin May, Chief Scientific
OL,7,FOfficer at the UK Health Security
OL,8,FAgency speaks to Kate Garraway and
OL,9,FRichard Madeley on Good Morning Britain
OL,11,FA British man evacuated from the
OL,12,Fhantavirus-hit cruise ship is "doing
OL,13,Fwell", health officials have said.
OL,15,FOn Wednesday, the World Health
OL,16,FOrganisation (WHO) said three
OL,17,Fsuspected hantavirus patients had been
OL,18,Fevacuated from the MV Hondius and
OL,19,Fflown to receive specialist medical
OL,20,Fcare in the Netherlands.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
