OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778193328
OL,3,CBritish crew member evacuated from
OL,4,Chantavirus ship 'doing well'
OL,6,FAmong them was Martin Anstee, 56, an
OL,7,Fexpedition guide and former police
OL,8,Fofficer, who was airlifted off the
OL,9,Fship along with Dutch and German
OL,10,Fpassengers.
OL,12,FProfessor Robin May, Chief Scientific
OL,13,FOfficer at the UK Health Security
OL,14,FAgency (UKHSA) confirmed to Good
OL,15,FMorning Britain that "he is receiving
OL,16,Fmedical care in the Netherlands and
OL,17,Four understanding is that he is doing
OL,18,Fwell and has spoken to friends and
OL,19,Ffamily".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778193328
OL,3,CBritish crew member evacuated from
OL,4,Chantavirus ship 'doing well'
OL,6,FSpeaking to Sky News, Mr Anstee said
OL,7,F"I'm doing okay. I'm not feeling too
OL,8,Fbad. There are still lots of tests to
OL,9,Fbe done.
OL,11,F"I have no idea how long I'll be in
OL,12,Fthe hospital for. I'm in isolation at
OL,13,Fthe moment."
OL,15,FTwo British people who were on board
OL,16,Fthe cruise are self-isolating after
OL,17,Freturning to the UK.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778193328
OL,3,CBritish crew member evacuated from
OL,4,Chantavirus ship 'doing well'
OL,6,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,7,Fsaid that neither of those people are
OL,8,Freporting symptoms, and that several
OL,9,Fclose contacts of those on the boat
OL,10,Fare also being "offered support and
OL,11,Fare also self-isolating".
OL,13,FProf May said: "We believe the risk
OL,14,Ffrom asymptomatic people of
OL,15,Ftransmission is extremely low" and the
OL,16,Frisk to the public is very low.
OL,26,@rD@POUsD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778193328
OL,3,CBritish crew member evacuated from
OL,4,Chantavirus ship 'doing well'
OL,6,FThe Foreign Office is arranging a
OL,7,Fcharter flight so remaining Britons on
OL,8,Fboard the ship who are not displaying
OL,9,Fsymptoms can be repatriated once they
OL,10,Fdock in Tenerife, which is expected in
OL,11,Fthe next couple of days.
OL,13,FAccording to the UKHSA, none of the
OL,14,FBritish citizens on board are
OL,15,Fcurrently reporting symptoms, but are
OL,16,Fbeing closely monitored.
OL,18,FNineteen British nationals were listed
OL,19,Fas passengers on the cruise and four
OL,20,FBritish crew members. It was sailing
OL,21,Ffrom Argentina to Cape Verde.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778193328
OL,3,CBritish crew member evacuated from
OL,4,Chantavirus ship 'doing well'
OL,6,FProf May said: "For the individuals
OL,7,Fthat are on the ship at the moment,
OL,8,Fwe're working, obviously, to
OL,9,Frepatriate them as soon as we possibly
OL,10,Fcan.
OL,12,F"The Foreign Office is leading on
OL,13,Fthat, and once they're back, they're
OL,14,Fgoing to be asked to self-isolate."
OL,16,FThe general consensus for the self
OL,17,Fisolation period is "probably six
OL,18,Fweeks" and that it's "45 days that
OL,19,Fwe're likely to be recommending".
OL,26,@nD@POUyD@UOU{D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778193328
OL,3,CBritish crew member evacuated from
OL,4,Chantavirus ship 'doing well'
OL,6,FHe added that the "most extreme case
OL,7,Fof incubation" of hantavirus "may be
OL,8,Fup to eight weeks".
OL,10,FHe also said: "We'll continue to
OL,11,Fsupport them and their families whilst
OL,12,Fthey self isolate, probably at home,
OL,13,Fbut obviously depends very much on the
OL,14,Findividual circumstances, depending on
OL,15,Fwhere they live and who they live
OL,16,Fwith, as to what the most appropriate
OL,17,Fmechanism is for them to self-isolate
OL,18,Ffor the next 45 days."
OL,26,@nD@SOUoD@NO]oD@^OUpD@RO]zD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778193328
OL,3,CBritish crew member evacuated from
OL,4,Chantavirus ship 'doing well'
OL,6,FProf May explained that hantaviruses
OL,7,Fas a group are widespread around the
OL,8,Fworld.
OL,10,F"This one, in particular, the Andean
OL,11,Fstrain, is the only one for which
OL,12,Fthere is some evidence in the past of
OL,13,Fhuman to human transmission, and so
OL,14,Fthat's obviously our primary focus
OL,15,Fhere," he said.
OL,17,FHe added it has been studied intently
OL,18,Fbecause it is "such a severe disease"
OL,19,Fand there are efforts globally to try
OL,20,Fto develop vaccines against it.
OL,26,@rD@AOUwD@FO]zD@OOUzD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
