OL,3,CBritish crew member evacuated from
OL,4,Chantavirus ship 'doing well'
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper said
OL,12,Fon Wednesday the Foreign Office is
OL,13,F"working urgently" to help get Britons
OL,14,F"safely home with proper protection
OL,15,Ffor public health".
OL,17,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting added:
OL,18,F"The outbreak of hantavirus on the MV
OL,19,FHondius will be worrying many.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@RO]vD@AOUwD@RO]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
