PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778193328
OL,3,CBritish crew member evacuated from
OL,4,Chantavirus ship 'doing well'
OL,6,F"The government are taking this
OL,7,Fincredibly seriously and are working
OL,8,Furgently to support the British
OL,9,Fnationals involved."
OL,11,FThree passengers have died on the MV
OL,12,FHondius following the hantavirus
OL,13,Foutbreak.
OL,15,FDespite concerns from locals and
OL,16,Fofficials, Spanish authorities have
OL,17,Fgiven permission for the ship to dock
OL,18,Fin the Canary Islands.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@TO]
